    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2>스코프</h2>\n<h3>개념</h3>\n<p>변수가 영향력을 발휘할 수 있는 범위를 말한다</p>\n<br>\n<p>scope 자체가 전역 변수와 지역 변수를 구분 짓는 역할</p>\n<br>\n<p>모든 영역에 영향력을 발휘할 수 있는 스코프를 전역 스코프 라고 한다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> globalVariable <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'전역변수'</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">func</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>globalVariable<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 사용 가능</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>지역 스코프는 함수나 블록 안에서만 영향력을 발휘할 수 있는 스코프</p>\n<br>\n<p>var은 사용 안하길 권장하니 사실상 블록 안에서만 영향력을 발휘한다고 생각하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'블록 스코프 안'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// i is not defined</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>주의점</h3>\n<p>함수는 서로의 스코프에 접근할 수 없다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> apple <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'사과'</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token function\">a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>apple<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token function\">b</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>잘못된 생각</p>\n<br>\n<p>b함수에서 a함수를 호출시 apple 변수가 a() 안에 있으니 사용가능하지 않을까?</p>\n<br>\n<p>함수호출과는 전혀 상관없다</p>\n<br>\n<p>apple이라는 변수가 영향력을 발휘할 수 있는 범위는 함수호출과는 상관없이 그 함수 안 뿐이다</p>\n<h2>스코프 체인</h2>","fields":{"slug":"/Vanila JS/2021-09-30 Scope/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Scope(스코프)","summary":"스코프, 스코프 체인, 렉시컬 스코핑","date":"2021.09.30.","categories":["Vanila","Javascript"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gat